### GET request to example server
GET https://examples.http-client.intellij.net/get
    ?generated-in=IntelliJ IDEA

### Obtener todas las bebidas (listado)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/drinks/0/page
Content-Type: application/json
# Respuesta: Lista de GetDrinkDTO (id, name, mililiters, alcohol, photo, units, state)

### Crear una bebida
POST http://localhost:8080/api/drinks/{categoryId}/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Jugo de Mango",
  "description": "Delicioso jugo de mango natural",
  "mililiters": 500,
  "alcohol": false,
  "photos": ["https://example.com/jugo1.jpg"],
  "units": 10
}

### Obtener detalle de una bebida
GET http://localhost:8080/api/drinks/{id}
Content-Type: application/json
# Respuesta: GetDrinkDetailDTO (id, name, description, mililiters, alcohol, photo, units, state, categoryName)

### Actualizar una bebida
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/drinks/{id}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Jugo de Mango",
  "description": "Delicioso jugo de mango natural recien hecho",
  "mililiters": 500,
  "alcohol": false,
  "photos": ["https://example.com/jugo1.jpg"],
  "units": 15
}

### Eliminar una bebida
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/drinks/{id}
